HEADWORD: Gastropneumatic
<hw>Gas`tro*pneu*mat"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Gastro-</ets> + <ets>pneumatic</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to the alimentary canal and air
